{"answer":"Okay, let's figure out what 2 plus 2 is!\n\n**Problem:** We want to find the total when we add 2 and 2.\n\n**Step-by-step reasoning:**\n1.  Imagine you have 2 items. For example, two apples.\n2.  Now, you add 2 more items. So, you get two more apples.\n3.  To find the total, we count all the apples together: one, two, three, four.\n\n**Final Answer:**\n2 + 2 = 4\n\n**Tip to check your result:**\nYou can use your fingers! Hold up 2 fingers on one hand, and 2 fingers on your other hand. Now, count all the fingers you have held up to see if you get the same answer.","model":"gemini-2.5-flash"}
